works.description:
Our published mobile app "Big Button Box 

Pro" is infringed by the graphics taken from "Big Button Box Pro" and used
 
in the app "Big Button Soundbox - 100+ FX" and its icon including but not 

limited to the following button graphics: Burp, Fart, Excuse Me!, Crash,  

Yee-Hah, Vomit, Yes, Grenade, Shut Up!, Elephant, Laughter, Cough, Rubber 

Ducky, Snore, Gimme Gimme, Pig, Aww Man!, Fail!, Hello, Goodbye, What?!,  

Bullet, Kazoo, Really?, Spit, Maybe, Bugle Call, Whoopee Cushion, Xylo,  
Clown Laugh, Angry Cat, Good Morning, Bike Bell, Smoke Alarm, Go!, Bugle  

Charge.

Additionally, our published mobile app "Big Button Box Pro" is infringed
by  
the marketing text used for "Big Button Soundbox - 100+ FX"  
including "There's nothing more satisfying than pressing a massive button 

and hearing a cool extra-loud, over-amplified, ear-piercing sound... and  

this app let's you do this over and over and over!"
